            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-2"></div>
                <div class=" col-8 lead jumbotron float-center" id="textbox" style="padding: 2%;">
                    A template for the PIP Server is a simple text file that has
                    data names from ISIS mixed inbetween the actual figure description. They use the name of the ISIS data 
                    those data names then get processed and exchanged with the data if they are found. 
                    The purpose of this is to allow users to reuse captions for multiple figures and this allows users to
                    use ISIS data in figure captions much faster than before. 
                </div>
